79
00:08:19,927 --> 00:08:22,293
I didn't do it for money!

80
00:08:23,597 --> 00:08:24,859
It's for my losing the game.

81
00:08:25,666 --> 00:08:26,428
It's too much!

82
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:30,636
Take it as your bonus,
since I enjoyed your company.

83
00:08:31,471 --> 00:08:33,234
I prefer something more lasting!

84
00:08:34,007 --> 00:08:36,066
I don't like it if it's
the last time with you.

85
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,477
What do you want then?

86
00:08:38,979 --> 00:08:39,775
One more night.

87
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,342
In your place this time!

88
00:08:43,617 --> 00:08:44,447
Suit yourself.

89
00:08:46,153 --> 00:08:46,949
Wow.

90
00:08:47,521 --> 00:08:49,421
You live here?

91
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:51,652
Amazing!

92
00:08:55,329 --> 00:08:55,852
Huh?

93
00:08:59,599 --> 00:09:00,497
Mr. Foster...

94
00:09:01,735 --> 00:09:03,259
Welcome back, Foster.

95
00:09:03,937 --> 00:09:04,926
Who is the lady?

96
00:09:05,072 --> 00:09:05,663
She's my guest.

97
00:09:06,506 --> 00:09:07,302
Show her a room.

98
00:09:16,249 --> 00:09:16,681
Clair.

99
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:17,548
Yes.

100
