174
00:16:45,999 --> 00:16:48,934
Myuha, how's Aisha's training going?

175
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,431
Well, she's showing some progress.

176
00:16:52,906 --> 00:16:53,531
I see.

177
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:02,908
She always looks so stunning.

178
