Don't touch me!

196
00:21:19,906 --> 00:21:20,873
I'm sorry.

197
00:21:22,809 --> 00:21:23,867
Don't get me wrong.

198
00:21:24,877 --> 00:21:28,313
I'm not angry at that guest, but at you!

199
00:21:29,182 --> 00:21:29,614
What?

200
00:21:30,249 --> 00:21:31,614
