204
00:21:48,501 --> 00:21:49,934
I'll get some water.

205
00:21:56,008 --> 00:21:56,872
Clair...

206
00:22:06,486 --> 00:22:07,510
I'm sorry, Clair.

207
00:22:09,155 --> 00:22:10,520
I said too much.

208
00:22:17,697 --> 00:22:18,288
Foster.

209
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:21,396
Are you well now?

210
00:22:22,535 --> 00:22:23,365
Don't try too hard.

211
00:22:26,038 --> 00:22:26,868
