230
00:25:31,424 --> 00:25:32,015
Right.

231
00:25:33,426 --> 00:25:33,790
Ren?

232
00:25:34,026 --> 00:25:34,424
Yes?

233
00:25:34,894 --> 00:25:37,055
Do you know
the phrase of a carnation?

234
00:25:37,496 --> 00:25:38,394
