235
00:25:38,864 --> 00:25:39,558
Passionate love.

236
00:25:40,333 --> 00:25:41,163
Pure love.

237
00:25:41,734 --> 00:25:43,224
I'm impressed, Aisha!

238
00:25:43,869 --> 00:25:44,528
Is that correct?

239
00:25:45,204 --> 00:25:45,636
Yes.

240
00:25:46,305 --> 00:25:47,499
